messages.message: I am trying to build my skills can you +1 me for a bunch?
I wonder if this affects search ranking in LinkedIn.
I am not sure about it. I think it is more of how many connections you have, in what industry and the position and job description you held
And the length of your profile
Probably, once you have been found.  But I think a lot recruiting software just does boolean matching.
Do you write that kind of stuff for TEK Systems?
I worked on several kinds and types of applications but not yet on a social networking site for job board like LinkedIn

I just said those reasoning based on my experience with LinkedIn. I was not taking LinkedIn seriously before and not even updating my profile but recruiters always found a way to find me back then even when I was a mid level developer in my career
Yeah I never took it seriously either and recently went through a transformation. Now I am writing a robot to help me prioritize my socializing.
